name: OBSIDIAN Do You Ever Get Lonely In The Dark

metadata.name: Obsidian no.1
metadata.description:
"Do you ever get lonely in the dark?"


Obsidian is a collaborative collection with Alice Wong (twitter: @the_defrag)

She paints the abstract in oil, and I do the figurative: it's like a slow dance between two artists. 

This artwork only exists in this digital form and does not exist in any other format anywhere else.
